in the DocumentRoot directory place a file called vhost.config
structure it in a format like .git/config

[description]
    this application runs free
[servers]
    this application needs
    server 1
    server 2
[ide]
    pycharm|idea|webstorm|phpstorm

legacy vhosts client's offered a mix of special comment lines in .conf
plus these two files in DocumentRoot: descrtiption and servers

NB wsgi applications don't have DocumentRoot - use Directory instead
